Quickstrike:




Quickstrike left Rattrap to Paralysis. He left the ship's auto-guns 
and shields on. He headed out in beast mode, and traveled to the 
location of the base. He still kept a careful eye out, since to him 
no day would be safe alone, and being Predacon. A battle could always 
start. 

Past the distance, he came across a downed ship. It had to be the 
base Black Arachnia had told him. He transformed to robot mode and 
looked around. He watched for the auto-guns. They better know he was 
coming.
